Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.41,0:00:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1500)\pos(424,430)}{\1a&H50&\2a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&\be1\b0\fs-4}{\K100}獻給曾經喜愛這世界的人們\N\N\N{\K200}{\K150}曾經與這世界的同伴歡度時光的人們\N\N\N{\K250}{\K150}呈現給這重逢的此刻——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.75,0:01:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tseng
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.47,0:01:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺真不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.49,0:01:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 總之快一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reno 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.84,0:02:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩 快離開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 那是誰?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Elena
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Life Stream
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.83,0:03:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是圍繞著星球的生命之河
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.08,0:03:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星球和生息在星球上所有生物的生命源泉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神羅公司
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.27,0:03:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了把Life Stream當作能源使用的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了它 使我們的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變的非常富裕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也有很多人認為
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種方法會導致星球的毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神羅對於反對他的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用武力鎮壓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:03:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神羅擁有被稱作Soldier的特別士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.30,0:04:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs-3}Soldier：神羅公司治安維持部門的最強部隊對其所屬人員的稱呼。\N由強至弱共分1st、2nd、3rd三個等級。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.22,0:03:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被移植了很久以前從天而降
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:04:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企圖毀滅這個星球帶來災厄的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.08,0:04:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JENOVA的細胞的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他們之中有一個叫Sephiroth的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常優秀的Soldier
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 在他獲知自己是由如此可怕的實驗而誕生的事實之後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從此開始憎恨神羅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不知何時 他開始憎恨這一切的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.34,0:04:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神羅 以及反神羅的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於過度憎恨 連星球都想破壞的Sephiroth
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和全力阻止Sephiroth的人們之間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了無數次的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無數的戰鬥也伴隨著無數的悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最喜歡的人也化成了Life Stream的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後在那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運之日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終結這一切戰爭的是星球自身的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星球把Life Stream當作武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湧現到地面的Life Stream
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.32,0:05:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把所有的爭鬥 野心 悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,統統吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以悲傷換來這一切 全部都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.77,0:05:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的說法是從兩年前開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這個星球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我們所想像的要更加更加憤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星痕綜合症
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 Marlene
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.66,0:06:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.57,0:06:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不要把Denzel帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不在了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好 這裡是衝擊貨運公司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs-3}The Strike Life Delivery Service
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本公司什麼都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.75,0:07:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問是哪一位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然記得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.49,0:08:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reno從Healin打電話過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是有工作要拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud 還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留言結束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kadaj 那就是哥哥的城市嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.31,0:09:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.74,0:09:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想他會歡迎我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.48,0:09:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別哭喔 Yazoo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽也在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別哭啊 Loz
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 哥哥來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是哥哥你藏了起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說你在騙我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然媽媽還是在你那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想跟你浪費唇舌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我接社長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.51,0:12:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我 Barret 成功了 我找到新的油田了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,油 田 那可真大的不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作差不多完了 再過不久就要去見Marlene了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我問候一下 回頭見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reno又打電話來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說很緊急
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總覺得有點奇怪 當心一點喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你厲害 服了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酷啊 Rude
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是曾經自稱Soldier的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來功夫沒有退步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是Rufus？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真是倒楣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找我有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大廈倒塌時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊我的人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.52,0:14:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算是保住一命…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助我一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們神羅欠世界一筆很大的債務
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把世界搞成這副悽慘模樣的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被說是我們引起的也不為過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 無論如何也要還清這筆帳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開門啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們開始針對Sephiroth所留下的影響展開調查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在北方的大空洞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜發現了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以放心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 發生了令人出乎意料之外的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.50,0:14:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人阻撓我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.97,0:14:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊你的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Kadaj一行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kadaj
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的目的好像就是要阻止我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.98,0:15:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 真不知道他們在想些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.15,0:15:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會被襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我們的同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kadaj一行既年輕又殘暴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.59,0:15:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們的結論要是僱用一名身手非凡的保鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作是送貨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你沒有其他人選
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你 原Soldier Cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.27,0:15:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我自稱的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"媽媽"是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.99,0:15:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kadaj說了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這年頭 懷念母親的小孩多的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說你跟孤兒們住在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想讓那些孩子們重拾笑容嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:16:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的最終目的 是重建一個新的世界 Cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託啦 Cloud 重建神羅公司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.26,0:16:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reno
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.32,0:16:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud住在這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.29,0:16:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.26,0:17:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Denzel一樣 Cloud也生病了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為生病才離家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.76,0:17:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他準備一個人去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他根本不打算戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tifa
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧 Marlene
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我想見Cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想見面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見面以後要做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.76,0:18:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起回家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前得好好說他一頓是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 下次我會實話實說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那似乎是在擺脫你們的途中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從直昇機上掉了下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.72,0:18:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很蠢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我發誓也行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就向這個發誓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.01,0:18:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.48,0:18:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要媽媽的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再結成時必須要用到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:18:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再結成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.88,0:18:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs-3}ReUnion：再結成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓擁有媽媽細胞的夥伴們再次齊聚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後向這星球復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然準備的很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.59,0:19:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有人把媽媽給藏了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說準備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星痕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長你也很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是多虧在Life Stream裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽遺傳思念的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻連媽媽在哪都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.59,0:19:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很慚愧 但這也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.66,0:19:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們只不過是思念體而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再找到媽媽賦予我們細胞為止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是變不回原樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有思念和星痕還是不夠完美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以為了真正的結合
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:20:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長 你早就發覺到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會連你的份也好好活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:20:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想當Soldier？ 加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.60,0:21:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 感覺怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.66,0:21:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了Midgar 你有什麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是朋友 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.68,0:21:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.68,0:21:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.09,0:21:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.39,0:22:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問妳 媽媽在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.93,0:22:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡沒有人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就來玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.39,0:22:26.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來可以大玩一場了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.23,0:23:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tifa
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.10,0:24:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.77,0:24:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒哭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.24,0:24:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.71,0:24:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把她帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.18,0:24:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.10,0:25:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.44,0:25:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.32,0:25:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有星痕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.46,0:25:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人能治好你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.81,0:26:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tifa
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.38,0:26:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tifa
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.52,0:26:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來得太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.99,0:26:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.76,0:26:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.20,0:27:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marlene
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.17,0:27:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.51,0:28:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.25,0:28:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和孩子們住在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.02,0:28:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻沒半個人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.86,0:28:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擔心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.70,0:28:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.61,0:28:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不坦白
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.27,0:29:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哥哥藏了起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.03,0:29:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由Life Stream誕生的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.17,0:29:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這魔石將賜與我們新的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.30,0:29:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reno他們出去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.81,0:29:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是星痕綜合症吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.88,0:30:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得就這樣死去也無所謂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.22,0:30:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.65,0:30:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有治療方法
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.69,0:30:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 Denzel很努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.16,0:30:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要逃避 要不要一起戰鬥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.50,0:30:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家互相幫助 一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.90,0:30:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為不是真正的家人 才不願意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.14,0:30:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.04,0:30:34.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也救不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.51,0:30:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是家人 或是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.35,0:30:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.69,0:30:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖拖拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.56,0:30:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖拖拉拉的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.50,0:30:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要拖到什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.70,0:30:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒找到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.60,0:31:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有目擊者看到是他們帶走的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.87,0:31:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶到哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.25,0:31:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺忘之都
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.31,0:31:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏匿處
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.20,0:31:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從媽媽那裡得到了特殊的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.20,0:31:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賦予人類痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.33,0:31:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及與這星球戰鬥的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.84,0:31:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實這種力量大家也都擁有
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.78,0:31:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.08,0:31:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們都是兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.45,0:31:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼承了融合在Life Stream裡
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.12,0:31:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被選上繼承媽媽遺傳思念的兄弟們
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.99,0:31:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.96,0:32:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這星球正阻撓著大家
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.66,0:32:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正打算阻止我們的成長
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.94,0:32:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你們的身體會感到疼痛 內心會受到挫折
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.74,0:32:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會治好你們
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.71,0:32:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後到媽媽的身邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.48,0:32:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們家族齊心合力 一起向這星球復仇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.83,0:32:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.67,0:33:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Denzel
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.25,0:33:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Denzel
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.16,0:34:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.96,0:34:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己都快撐不住了 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.36,0:34:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會好轉的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.93,0:34:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.42,0:34:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要來這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.47,0:34:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 想得到原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.45,0:34:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我想得到原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.87,0:34:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向誰呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.93,0:35:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是來了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.68,0:35:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來接孩子們回家
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.10,0:35:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人啊 是我們的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.09,0:35:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 很可惜的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.45,0:35:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.69,0:35:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.68,0:38:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的都無法得救嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.50,0:38:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vincent 到底發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.39,0:38:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我經常來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.85,0:38:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以看到了Kadaj的事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.07,0:38:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星痕
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.05,0:38:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有能排除侵入體內異分子擴散的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.82,0:38:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體內也會有像Life Stream的結構
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.84,0:38:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此會跟入侵體內的邪惡分子對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.44,0:38:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪惡分子
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.87,0:38:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sephiroth因子 JENOVA的遺傳思念
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.22,0:38:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你怎麼稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.69,0:38:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的很詳細啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.81,0:38:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tseng和Elena
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.81,0:38:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在奄奄一息的狀態下被帶來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.24,0:39:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受了不少殘酷的拷問
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.71,0:39:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然救了他們
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.70,0:39:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道現在怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.67,0:39:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拷問
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.37,0:39:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.92,0:39:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們似乎把JENOVA的人頭弄到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.00,0:39:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kadaj所尋找的媽媽就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.12,0:39:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從天而降的凶神
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.41,0:39:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JENOVA
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.93,0:39:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要他們願意 就可以再次創造出一個Sephiroth
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.75,0:39:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kadaj
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.86,0:39:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.57,0:39:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.83,0:39:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marlene
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.89,0:39:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud Denzel他？ Tifa她？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.37,0:39:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tifa沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.87,0:39:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想見Tifa
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.16,0:39:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有帶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.34,0:40:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.15,0:40:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vincent 能不能把Marlene送回店裡
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.78,0:40:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找神羅他們
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.82,0:40:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不贊成這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.83,0:40:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.61,0:40:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了Cloud
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.92,0:40:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你就不肯聽我們的話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.99,0:40:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marlene
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.68,0:40:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.43,0:40:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想戰鬥馬上就會開始
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.68,0:40:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 光只戰鬥是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.95,0:40:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.74,0:40:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.29,0:40:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud 你打算開戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.74,0:40:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.89,0:40:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遺忘之都
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.91,0:40:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏匿處
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.77,0:40:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.72,0:40:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去跟Rufus談談
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.28,0:40:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.53,0:40:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.67,0:41:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算找到孩子們可能也無能為力
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.46,0:41:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能會造成無法挽回的後果
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.09,0:41:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你害怕會變成這樣對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.42,0:41:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在你應該接受更多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.22,0:41:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很沉重嗎 因為那沉重到無法承受
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.31,0:41:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非得要一個人來你才能忍下去
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.91,0:41:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很厭惡孤單對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.36,0:41:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不肯接電話卻死抓著不放
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.94,0:41:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去藏匿處吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.08,0:41:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們輸給了回憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.65,0:41:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為我曾經視而不顧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.07,0:41:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是拖拖拉拉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.92,0:41:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.23,0:41:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候原諒自己了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.42,0:42:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過錯… 能被原諒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.01,0:42:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒試過
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.77,0:42:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘗試？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.87,0:42:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘗試
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.02,0:42:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marlene 我們回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.98,0:42:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.15,0:42:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果我會通知你
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.60,0:42:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是里布 工作的怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.57,0:42:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看過廣告了 但那東西真能賺錢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.05,0:42:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然那很適合Cloud先生就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.70,0:42:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話我也想幫忙 所以再連絡
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.10,0:42:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Reno從Healin打電話來 說是有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.84,0:42:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見 是我 Yuffie
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.14,0:43:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wutai的孩子們都不見了 你知道是怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.81,0:43:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道些事情的話 拜託你告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.21,0:43:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樣子有點奇怪 當心點
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.84,0:43:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從不覺得你有對不起我
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.49,0:43:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是來了嗎 這樣就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.92,0:44:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你聽到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.42,0:44:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.80,0:44:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Denzel
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.37,0:44:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Denzel
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.64,0:45:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Denzel
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.73,0:45:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.24,0:45:35.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽就在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.65,0:45:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.05,0:45:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個叫什麼紀念碑的 是神羅建的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.39,0:45:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 還會動頭腦耶
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.02,0:45:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你們猜錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.18,0:45:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.34,0:45:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會相信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.24,0:46:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.19,0:46:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 Kadaj
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.31,0:46:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.10,0:46:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一件喔
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.48,0:46:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過 只要弄到JENOVA的細胞就能恢復原狀
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.14,0:46:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.47,0:46:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"他"將會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.96,0:46:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sephiroth
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.99,0:46:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是惡夢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.88,0:46:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是的
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.26,0:46:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.84,0:46:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道Sephiroth
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.27,0:46:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有感覺到而已
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.69,0:46:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我感到急躁
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.39,0:46:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽是會選擇我 還是Sephiroth
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.32,0:46:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐的思念體
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.99,0:47:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論如何你們的結果都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.13,0:47:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽是經過了漫長的旅途才來到這星球
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.14,0:47:09.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了將愚蠢的事物從宇宙中消除
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.11,0:47:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你也知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.95,0:47:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡和媽媽到來時一點都沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.48,0:47:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想讓媽媽高興
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.44,0:47:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是媽媽的命令我什麼都幹
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.06,0:47:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 重演惡夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.89,0:47:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有你們在 不管什麼事都會一而再的重複
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.10,0:47:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圍繞著星球的Life Stream
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.37,0:47:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷在生死之間來回
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.04,0:47:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說那輪迴才是生命的原型的話
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.34,0:47:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重蹈覆轍的歷史就是必然的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.93,0:47:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是JENOVA還是Sephiroth
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.14,0:47:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就隨你們喜歡做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.49,0:48:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會聽從命運的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.69,0:48:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會一次又一次的阻止你們
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.76,0:48:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長 這就是你們搶走媽媽的藉口嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.23,0:48:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你該不會是很後悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.27,0:48:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後悔？ 我可是快樂的不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.49,0:48:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 那麼差不多也該結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.54,0:49:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Denzel 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.36,0:50:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.80,0:50:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.04,0:50:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.70,0:51:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追來了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.31,0:51:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.15,0:51:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愉快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.98,0:51:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愉快個頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.86,0:51:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們太頑固了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.46,0:52:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了嗎 只要把媽媽交出來這一切就都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.27,0:52:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.85,0:52:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用JENOVA的頭想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.29,0:52:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再結成什麼的 是認真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.46,0:52:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只不過是想見媽媽而已
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.67,0:52:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽將會決定今後的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.20,0:52:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.28,0:53:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽媽媽的 還不就是JENOVA而已
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.86,0:53:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.93,0:53:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許你這樣說媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.96,0:53:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.33,0:53:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.77,0:53:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊… 幹嘛要道歉啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.99,0:54:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tifa
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.30,0:54:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.14,0:54:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在這照顧媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.05,0:54:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Barret
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.55,0:54:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marlene沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.10,0:54:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.83,0:55:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰用了我的魔石？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.80,0:55:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.54,0:55:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帳
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.04,0:55:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.62,0:55:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型的Sierra號
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.06,0:55:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會讓你上去坐坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.56,0:55:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通訊行在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.13,0:55:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.30,0:55:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.71,0:56:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marlene沒事 我把她放在店裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.98,0:56:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.88,0:56:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得輕鬆了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.05,0:56:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.39,0:56:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是拖拖拉拉的時候磨輕了的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.03,0:56:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.90,0:56:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Marlene一起等著
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.30,0:56:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud也會回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.29,0:58:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.89,0:59:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太愉快了 社長 接下來再召喚什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.69,0:59:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.70,1:00:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不肖子 該早點發現啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.12,1:00:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 Cloud
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.42,1:00:28.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一把
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.08,1:00:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.30,1:00:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.33,1:00:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.02,1:01:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.21,1:01:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.06,1:02:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.90,1:02:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.08,1:06:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說搭檔
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.05,1:06:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 很厲害嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.09,1:06:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集合了神羅的技術製作
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.59,1:07:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你做的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.10,1:07:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不說威力 漂亮的很
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.97,1:07:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇喔
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.37,1:07:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜歡吧 搭擋
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.52,1:07:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來今天不必加班了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.05,1:08:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.80,1:08:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.23,1:08:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.27,1:10:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 Cloud
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.20,1:11:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於見到媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.32,1:11:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要如何開始
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.81,1:11:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽會告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.82,1:11:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念體什麼都不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.54,1:11:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我只不過是個被操縱的玩偶
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.87,1:11:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和以前的你
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.66,1:11:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.66,1:12:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud 我拿魔石來了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.43,1:12:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別搖啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.63,1:12:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 Cid 快點降下去
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.34,1:12:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 想下去自己跳下去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.60,1:12:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓他一個人戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.15,1:12:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.77,1:12:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是Sephiroth的思念體
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.97,1:12:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是幼蟲一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.04,1:12:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼蟲？ 蟲子？ 那傢伙是蟲子？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.45,1:12:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姑娘 別激動
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.08,1:12:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天會變成Sephiroth嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.35,1:12:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.89,1:12:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.53,1:12:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:12:35.34,1:12:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就讓他一個人戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.77,1:12:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白 誰來說明一下
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.76,1:12:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人才會知道
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.22,1:12:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差別待遇 差別待遇!!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.18,1:12:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別激動 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.33,1:12:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人也不懂
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.43,1:12:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2年前
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.26,1:12:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最後一戰時確實擁有堅強的心
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.65,1:12:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但兩年的時光卻讓他遺忘了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.92,1:13:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 Cloud是想找回那心情
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.14,1:13:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呿 那就等他十分鐘吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.66,1:13:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud還是一樣那麼難伺候
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.27,1:13:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叫正直
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.71,1:14:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你見識見識 我的再結成
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.69,1:14:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了 Cloud
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.02,1:15:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星痕沒有了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.96,1:15:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.67,1:15:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底期望什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.77,1:15:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依宿星痕上死者的思念
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.50,1:15:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它和Life Stream一起圍繞著星球
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.30,1:15:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天開始侵蝕星球
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.80,1:15:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud 我的願望
Dialogue: 0,1:15:34.38,1:15:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是把這顆星球當作方舟 在黑暗的宇宙中旅行
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.78,1:15:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像媽媽過去所作的一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.82,1:15:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天我們會找到新的星球
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.26,1:15:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且在新的天地創造光輝的未來
Dialogue: 0,1:15:56.60,1:15:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這個星球會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.77,1:16:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天曉得 接下來就要看你了
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.89,1:16:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊？
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.01,1:17:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼讓你變強的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.47,1:17:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.53,1:17:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直考慮該送什麼給你
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.15,1:18:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送你"絕望"如何？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.36,1:18:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跪下吧 讓我看看你請求饒恕的模樣
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.65,1:19:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最重要的東西是什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.05,1:20:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我享受將它從你身邊奪走的喜悅吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.17,1:20:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可悲 你什麼都不明白
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.18,1:20:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有什麼不重要的事物
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.39,1:20:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在回憶中安息吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.01,1:20:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.58,1:21:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不會成為回憶的
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.56,1:21:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.26,1:21:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kadaj
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.91,1:21:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.21,1:21:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經很努力了 放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.93,1:22:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是… 媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.79,1:22:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到大家的身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.87,1:22:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.66,1:23:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他成功了 我就知道它一定行
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.15,1:23:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 我說得沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.67,1:23:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子漢 Cloud真是個男子漢
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.93,1:23:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud一定能辦到
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.93,1:23:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好好抓緊啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.25,1:23:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳一直… 都在我們身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.27,1:23:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.95,1:24:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起 回家吧
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.03,1:24:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家… 一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.18,1:25:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.49,1:25:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cloud 會回來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.72,1:26:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.66,1:26:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:06.06,1:26:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是他第幾次叫我媽媽啦
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.71,1:26:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這麼思念妳 又有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.26,1:26:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不要這麼大的孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.44,1:26:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可惜 看來這裡沒有你待的地方
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.88,1:27:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊她
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.47,1:27:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說Cloud會來這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.07,1:27:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你回來
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.43,1:27:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.27,1:27:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有星痕沒消失的孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.84,1:27:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.79,1:27:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 把它治好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.87,1:28:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.48,1:28:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.54,1:29:02.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 儘管跳下去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.39,1:29:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治好了治好了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.93,1:29:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒事了對吧
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.59,1:30:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.15,1:30:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.41,1:30:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再是一個人了